I have edited the scoutznknivez map into a jailbreak map for people's enjoyment. Thanks to *[ConvictS]* Servers for the inspiration, ideas, and help.
The O in convicts teleports to hospital.
On top of T is a deagle.
On top of S is Awp with sprite tail.
Shotgun in pool.
Vent from cells to pool.
Vents.
Big Cage.
Gun Room.
Anti Freekill in cells. (Terrorist are able to hide from CT Freekillers in the cells.)
The map inclues:
22 Terrorist.
17 Counter-Terrorist.
